cs.CR, cs.SE, cs.SY, cs.PL, cs.OS 

This paper focuses on investigating vulnerabilities in the Android operating system, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also mentions the importance of verification and validation activities for OS and app developers, which relates to software engineering (cs.SE) and system and control theory (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the layers and subsystems of the Android OS affected by vulnerabilities, which could fall under programming languages (cs.PL) and operating systems (cs.OS).
